OL,3,CTen ducklings rescued from storm drain
OL,5,FTen ducklings have been reunited with
OL,6,Ftheir mother after they became trapped
OL,7,Fin a storm drain in central Reading.
OL,9,FThey were spotted trying to escape the
OL,10,Fdrain on Castle Street after becoming
OL,11,Fseparated from their mother.
OL,13,FBerkshire Fire and Rescue crews
OL,14,Fattended and manage to free them with
OL,15,Fthe help of a bucket.
OL,17,FThey were then released safely into
OL,18,Fthe River Thames.
